    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[CreationTime], [o].[CreatorUserId], [o].[DeleterUserId], [o].[DeletionTime], [o].[IsDeleted], [o].[LastModificationTime], [o].[LastModifierUserId], [o].[Note], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserEmail], [o].[UserId], [o].[UserName], [o].[UserPhone]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [o].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [t].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id]
